---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy" description="ThingsBoard Cookie Policy">
	<div class="cookie-policy-page">
		<div class="cookie-policy-content">
			<h1>Cookie Policy</h1>

			<p>
				Cookies and Local Storage are activated and used during your browsing on this site. Cookies
				are small text files, usually numbers and letters, that do not create a security risk for
				your computer, tablet, or smartphone. Local Storage is a similar mechanism used to store
				data, such as UTM tags, directly in your browser.
			</p>

			<p>Cookies allow us to:</p>

			<ul>
				<li>
					Understand the behavior of visitors, measure the number of visits and page views using <a
						href="https://analytics.google.com/">Google Analytics</a
					>;
				</li>
				<li>
					Improve load-balancing and page load speed using <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/"
						>Cloudflare</a
					>.
				</li>
				<li>
					Enhance user experience and provide personalized features through <a
						href="https://yourgpt.ai/">YourGPT</a
					>, which uses cookies to analyze user interactions and improve service functionality.
				</li>
			</ul>

			<p>These cookies are enabled by default on your web browser.</p>
			<p>
				However, you may configure your browser to alert you each time cookies are created. It is
				also possible to prevent their installation. Here is the procedure to follow on the three
				main browsers:
			</p>

			<ul>
				<li>
					Chrome <a
						href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647?hl=en&co=GENIE.Platform%3DDesktop"
						>instructions</a
					>;
				</li>
				<li>
					Firefox <a
						href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/clear-cookies-and-site-data-firefox"
						>instructions</a
					>;
				</li>
				<li>
					Safari <a href="https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/manage-cookies-sfri11471/mac"
						>instructions</a
					>.
				</li>
			</ul>

			<p>
				Access to our site will not be denied if you disable cookies, but some features may not
				work.
			</p>

			<p>
				You may find below the additional information and resources regarding the above mentioned
				services.
			</p>

			<h3>Google Analytics</h3>
			<p>
				See Google Analytics privacy <a
					href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/cookies?hl=en-US">page</a
				> for more details.
			</p>

			<h3>Cloudflare</h3>
			<p>
				See Cloudflare documentation <a
					href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/fundamentals/reference/policies-compliances/cloudflare-cookies/"
					>page</a
				> for more details.
			</p>

			<h3>YourGPT</h3>
			<p>
				See YourGPT privacy <a href="https://yourgpt.ai/privacy">page</a> for more details.
			</p>

			<h3>Other Cookies</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<strong>cookie-notice-dismissed</strong> is used to store if the user clicked <code
						>Accept</code
					> button on the cookies banner or close (X) it. This cookie has a 365 days timeout.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>cloudServer</strong> is used to store the last visited cloud region in the
					documentation. Possible values: <code>/docs/paas/eu/</code> (EU cloud) or <code
						>/docs/paas/</code
					> (North America cloud). This allows us to automatically open the correct (EU or North
					America) version of the documentation on your next visit. This cookie has a 365 days
					timeout.
				</li>
			</ul>

			<p>
				Please note that by continuing to browse this site with the opened cookies banner, you
				agree the use of cookies, in accordance with our cookie policy.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style lang="scss">
	@use '../../styles/variables' as *;

	.cookie-policy-page {
		min-height: 100vh;
		background-color: #fff;
	}

	.cookie-policy-content {
		max-width: 860px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 60px 24px 80px;
		color: #212529;
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-size: 16px;
		text-align: justify;

		h1 {
			font-size: 32px;
			font-weight: 600;
			margin-bottom: 24px;
		}

		h3 {
			font-size: 20px;
			font-weight: 600;
			margin: 32px 0 8px;

			&::before {
				display: none;
			}
		}

		p {
			margin: 0 0 12px;
		}

		ul {
			margin: 0 0 12px;
			padding-left: 24px;
			list-style: disc;

			li {
				margin-bottom: 4px;
				list-style: disc;
				color: #75767c;
				font-size: 1.125rem;
				line-height: 1.6;

				&::marker {
					color: #75767c;
				}
			}
		}

		a {
			color: #2a7dec;
			text-decoration: none;

			&:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
		}

		code {
			background: #f4f4f4;
			padding: 2px 6px;
			border-radius: 4px;
			font-size: 14px;
		}
	}
</style>
